---
title: Mumbai Chickpea & Roast Veggie Curry with Garlic Rice & Coriander
description: If you’ve been looking for a dinner that involves little effort but packs a flavoursome punch then we have something just for you. Roasting an array of colourful veggies is an instant winner and a great way to boost any curry. Stir them through a tomato spiced curry sauce, mild and with notes of ginger, to allow everything to blend into one big bowl of deliciousness.

